data.text: Laís Pereira de Oliveira, famous as Lais Ribeiro is a model and social media personality from Brazil. She is popular for being one of the Angels of Victoria’s Secret. Lais was a professional nurse in Brazil. Some of her friends advised her to pursue a career in modeling because her physique was up to the mark for modeling. In 2009 she started locally modeling, later that year she walked for major designers like Dolce & Gabbana, Blumarine, and many more.
